

Installing Adafruit_GPIO
for python2 : > pip install Adafruit_GPIO
for python3 ; > pip3.2 install Adafruit_GPIO

Activating I2C :
> sudo raspi-config
then : 5 Interface option
then : P5 I2C Enable/Disable automatic loading
then : Yes/Oui
Then : Ok
Then : Finish

Use of ServoBlaster from PiBits : https://github.com/richardghirst/PiBits
Installing Servo Blaster : 
> git clone https://github.com/richardghirst/PiBits.git
> cd PiBits/ServoBlaster/user/
> sudo make install

Get PythonSB.py from : https://github.com/jabelone/pythonSB

Use of jQuery-Flight-Indicator from : https://github.com/sebmatton/jQuery-Flight-Indicators
> git clone https://github.com/sebmatton/jQuery-Flight-Indicators
